1578
01:11:06,540 --> 01:11:07,240
Ele já é o suficiente.

1579
01:11:10,880 --> 01:11:11,320
Beleza.

1580
01:11:17,860 --> 01:11:18,300
Valentina

1581
01:11:18,300 --> 01:11:19,700
